Partly cloudy. Winds calm. 7 fishing boats. Lots of Curly Leaf and Collapsing millpond surfacing.  Few seagulls- geese and babies present. Sky is partly cloudy. Calm.   7 boats on the lake.  Curly leaf surfacing.......lots.  Seagulls and geese and babies.
Cloudy day.  Algae floating.  Lilly pads starting to bloom. One boat on the lake.  Geese- terns and seagulls pressent.  Eurasian Millfoil present.  Curly leaf receded to bottom.

column1: No signs of pan fish spawning.  Several families of geese.

column2: Partly cloudy.  Calm winds.  Extensive weeds:  curly leaf floating and submerged.  Filamentous algae prominent.

column1: 4 boaters fishing.  No seagulls.  A few tern.   Partly Cloudy- calm winds.  Lake has extensive floating and emerging weeds- mostly curly leaf.  Filamentous algae prominent in some areas.  North side of lake appears to have the more weeds make lake life rather sad.
Lily pads are not blooming yet.  No seagulls.  a few tern.  4 boaters fishing.

column2: Partly cloudy. Three boats on the lake. Lilly pads are blooming. Eurasian Milfoil emerging. Seagulls are abundant.
Warm day.  Sky is mostly clear.  Lots of Geese with goslings of various ages.  One pelican.  Tern.  Swallows.

column1: Lake is brown along shore but greener farther out.  Murky.  Water level is up a little.  Weeds are very prevalent.  Mostly curly leaf spreading to new areas from last year but still present in last years areas.   Large amounts of carp spawning.
Really disappointing to see how many carp there are in just a few years time.  Two boats.

column2: Shoreline is murky and green.  Deep Hole area is clear and green.  Large areas of matted algae clinging to weeds.  Coontail- collapsing millpond- eurasion.  More geese present than last year.  Lots of poop on the shore line. 8 boaters- 2 kayaks.  No fish kill noted.

Lake Emily is calm.  Sky is clear.  Large area of emergent weeds on the south side...pretty much impassible with a boat.  Appears to be Eurasian milfoil and coontail.   One fisherman out.  Seagulls.  Geese are not around today.
